    narr:narration """This roadmap hub continues to braid GTM strategy with technical implementation, though the focus has sharpened on the [train-the-trainers sequence](narr:DeckUpdate_GTMFraming) as the primary vehicle for early-stage viability. The [GTM validation](narr:Narrative_GTMValidation) reinforces this as a necessary pivot from pure consulting toward an upfront-revenue model, operationalized through a [three-phase beta](narr:Narrative_ThreePhaseBeta) that moves from content proof to process integration. The [technical implementation](narr:Obs_NextSteps) remains distinct, focusing on specific transactional and pipeline tooling rather than the broader architectural roadmap previously discussed. A [candid, colloquial register](narr:StyleObs_Colloquial) persists as the underlying tone, framing the commercial necessity of the roadmap with directness.""" ;
